trying to tell Cecilia I'm in love with her.

1095
01:10:48,369 --> 01:10:53,708
I love you. I'm honest, dependable,
courageous, romantic, and a great kisser.

1096
01:10:53,833 --> 01:10:56,628
- And I'm real.
