1097
01:10:56,753 --> 01:10:59,047
<i>Choose one of them,
so we can settle this thing.</i>

1098
01:10:59,172 --> 01:11:02,342
<i>The most human of attributes
is your ability to choose.</i>

1099
01:11:02,467 --> 01:11:06,220
<i>Wait a minute. If she chooses Tom,
how are we gonna end the story?</i>

1100
01:11:06,346 --> 01:11:10,391
<i>- We'll be stuck here for ever</i>
- Father Donnelly can marry us right here.

1101
01:11:10,516 --> 01:11:13,102
That won't stand up.
The priest has to be human.

1102
01:11:13,227 --> 01:11:15,688
<i>The Bible never says
a priest can't be on film.</i>

1103
01:11:15,813 --> 01:11:19,942
- No, I'm already married.
- Come away with me to Hollywood.

1104
01:11:20,068 --> 01:11:22,445
- Just like that?
- Just like that.

1105
01:11:22,570 --> 01:11:24,947
Do something impulsive
for once in your life.

1106
01:11:25,073 --> 01:11:28,868
Just throw your stuff in a valise
and come away with me. Really.

1107
01:11:28,993 --> 01:11:32,163
- And don't forget that ukulele.
- What ukulele?

1108
01:11:32,288 --> 01:11:38,294
Look, I love you. I know
that only happens in movies, but I do.

1109
01:11:42,799 --> 01:11:44,425
Tom...

1110
01:11:45,802 --> 01:11:50,306
<i>- You're throwing away perfection
- Don't tell her that. We need Tom back.</i>

1111
01:11:50,431 --> 01:11:53,142
<i>- It's so romantic.
